{"tid":1606083,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［急］［沙田友入］關於聽日嘅遊行...","createTime":"2019-09-30T13:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T15:53:18.000Z","uid":231478,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bcf917f589c1cb60fd15a96b61bef44c67b0c3ea","tid":1606083,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BOTtVTt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBOTtVTt.png&h=d021f219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首先 我聲明先 唔係想分化 唔係想叫人唔去<br />\n而係 人地都話跑馬唔會取消 <br />\n咁去嘅意義係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加上馬場附近就係火炭 工業區 行前d就到科學園（未到科學園之前仲有水狗總部）<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大埔嗰頭 都難走嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然話馬仔唔可以食tg 但唔排除班狗用其他武力架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如改下地點 針對政權好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起點時間可以唔改架 無洗驚文宣方面<br />\n利申：最後決定去馬場我都無所謂，點都唔割，香港人要一齊行！<br />\n有無沙田友可以傾下 比d意見 唔岩聽可以屌得細力d<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n沙田友加油！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b9c3fdcdafc57c23c58e1f293609356156571c53","tid":1606083,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:02:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac00518593e1f3e9e9d9e994281c9bfe43502ba6","tid":1606083,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:02:55.000Z","msg":"有無沙田友可以比下意見？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a970e51204e6369b7866eb7aae9a87dd22abda3","tid":1606083,"uid":270237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:03:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日出去前睇左先</span></span></span><br />\n來自CSD職員既提醒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1603297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1603297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n你班勇武手足,同我聽住,有部份前線手足認識我地,之前幾場戰役我地合作過,最初有人以為我地係鬼,詳細唔多講,我地係一班受過專業防暴訓練懲教署職員,之前已經係現場教過大家,如何組織防線同攻擊防暴,之前都有唔少進步,但今日我地冇出現,你地表現太差,中要咁多比人拉,我好心痛..<br />\n我地人手有限,身份問題,冇可能次次出現,我係度比些少資訊大家,希望大家務必share同發輝得好D<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1.速龍都係人,佢地咩住咁重裝備同蒙面先至令信心大增,但大家留意下佢地人手一定唔夠手足多,只要大家穩固防線,只要佢地一跑出嚟,手足唔走向前攻,先用人火同磚頭攻,再快速向前推進, 趁機會足幾個差人抬去自己方向,呢個時候繼續用磚頭攻擊,同時向差人方向口射洗潔精地下,務別令佢地仆街,最重要立即除佢哋面具,之後私了..佢地以後就會驚..</span></span><br />\n2.佩槍唔係向上蚊,而係向內45度角向前推,大家明點做😁<br />\n3.如果執到警槍,同佢地玩過遊戲,逐粒子彈唔小心跌落坑渠,洗手間,包保玩殘佢地...<br />\n4.咁黑仔有狗用槍指你,可行情況試下用1秒用長竹,或雨傘打佢手同向上..<br />\n5如果打狗,唔該搵手足集中打腳,上半身有盾牌你打係冇用,要傷腳同關節先有足,以上除左增強攻擊同防護能力之外,就係要令到狗驚,你要記住佢地都係人,唔係超人...<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">6.哨兵必須去遠少少,手足唔好集足一個地方,必須快速移動,不停向唔同地方攻擊,切斷差人增援,攻擊完立即走人,玩殘班狗..</span></span><br />\n7.盡量引班狗去橋下,用高空方式攻擊..<br />\n最後10.1見,大家努力<br />\n一班CSD職員上<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/StbvpQF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FStbvpQF.jpg&h=daf53d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zx5j2Cm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzx5j2Cm.jpg&h=731725ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba6654838977aed39d5c919e1b99d0b98080ab50","tid":1606083,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:03:19.000Z","msg":"有無人幫手推？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"364c3e43fcc494407f97d7e2c9e42e21a9c6105e","tid":1606083,"uid":29979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"大家聽日要有目標！唔好再賽跑啦！記得保護自己保護手足<br />\n<br />\n《終極軍師》勇武請入，十一「六區佔領政府部門」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1605991\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1605991</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e12691e3c5d566f0b364e4a0253dd9954f746c07","tid":1606083,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"自推 10"},{"pid":"c983a96bfb42ff804f92867489265e9c111c8799","tid":1606083,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:05:21.000Z","msg":"自推 9"},{"pid":"865970c90128d73bd5bc852285f2ecb3e03d70d5","tid":1606083,"uid":63117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:05:27.000Z","msg":"去得馬場預左要開波  太多廢老藍屍"},{"pid":"9b26d8d2edd19bde5c807f9aa639ba5378181b3d","tid":1606083,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:05:31.000Z","msg":"自推 8"},{"pid":"886177b65ae8526f0af337ab8d9840f86d01beb4","tid":1606083,"uid":231478,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"865970c90128d73bd5bc852285f2ecb3e03d70d5","tid":1606083,"uid":63117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:05:27.000Z","msg":"去得馬場預左要開波  太多廢老藍屍"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T13:07:17.000Z","msg":"但鶳嘅意義係 佢哋打人 我地先會用 唔係因為人地政見唔同 我地就要鶳人地啊嘛<br />\n利申：核爆都唔割"},{"pid":"f5ef4745109333b123de62a16222a3c6f6e61d47","tid":1606083,"uid":231478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30